<div id="pf28" class="pf w4 h2" data-page-no="28"><div class="pc pc28 w4 h2"><div class="t m1e x44 h1e y534 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">given for the benefit of the church as a whole, not merely to benefit the </div><div class="t m41e x44 h1e y535 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">individual. No one person has every gift. (See 1 Cor. 12:27-31.) Paul de-</div><div class="t m41f x44 h1e y570 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">clares that he would rather speak five words with understanding than ten </div><div class="t m77 x44 h1e y537 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thousand words in an unknown tongue. (See 1 Cor. 14:19.). </div><div class="t m420 x44 h1d y7 ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: </div><div class="t m29 x2f h1e y7 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Please summarize this lesson in your own words: </div><div class="t m421 x29 h1d y3be ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">APPLICATION </div><div class="t md8 x62 h1e y3bf ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Am I walking after the flesh or after the Spirit? </div><div class="t m422 x62 h1e y3c1 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Do I pray earnestly daily for the power of the Spirit to possess my </div><div class="t m37e x62 h1e y3c3 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">life and to use me in God&apos;s work? </div><div class="t m423 x31 h46 y571 ff6 fs23 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What Happened to Our </div><div class="t m1df x69 h46 y25a ff6 fs23 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Bible Book Studies? </div><div class="t m424 x31 h2d y572 ff5 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Bible book curriculum has been in-</div><div class="t m425 x31 h2d y573 ff5 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">terrupted in order to make it possible </div><div class="t m426 x31 h2d y574 ff5 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the world church to review the </div><div class="t m427 xac h2f y575 ff5 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">27 </div><div class="t m428 x31 h2d y576 ff5 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fundamental beliefs of Seventh-day </div><div class="t m429 x31 h2d y577 ff5 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Adventists. We resume our study of the </div><div class="t m42a x31 h2d y578 ff5 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Bible books beginning with the first </div><div class="t me2 x31 h2d y50d ff5 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">quarter of </div><div class="t m42b x4d h2f y50d ff5 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1989. </div><div class="t m161 x44 h1f y2d9 ff6 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">40 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
